## Step 8: Ansible Deployment

WSL Ubuntu:

Create Playbook

`deploy.yml`

```yaml
---
- name: Deploy Maven Artifact
  hosts: localhost

  tasks:

    - name: Create Deploy Folder
      file:
        path: /tmp/deploy
        state: directory

    - name: Copy Jar File
      copy:
        src: /mnt/c/Users/tejas/IdeaProjects/Experiment100/target/Experiment100-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar
        dest: /tmp/deploy/
```

Run:

```bash
ansible-playbook deploy.yml
```

